        "content": "<p>Inspired by a <a href=\"https://github.com/teorth/equational_theories/wiki/Terence-Tao's-personal-log\">similar log I wrote</a> for the equational theories project, I am starting a personal log to document the various things going on in this project, hopefully reducing some of the clutter in this Zulip.  Here is the first entry: <a href=\"https://github.com/AlexKontorovich/PrimeNumberTheoremAnd/wiki/Terence-Tao's-personal-log#day-2-jan-16-2026\">Day 2</a></p>",
