        "content": "<p><a href=\"https://github.com/AlexKontorovich/PrimeNumberTheoremAnd/wiki/Terence-Tao's-personal-log#day-4-jan-18-2026\">Day 4</a> <a href=\"https://github.com/AlexKontorovich/PrimeNumberTheoremAnd/wiki/Terence-Tao's-personal-log#day-5-jan-19-2026\">Day 5</a></p>",
